&lt;img src='https://terzeron.com/xml/img/1x1.jpg?feed=wikidocs_blog.xml&amp;item=5fe264a'/&gt;
</description><guid>https://wikidocs.net/blog/@K_Haku/224/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 02:17:24 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>파이썬으로 구현한 회전 정리 by zip( )</title><link>https://wikidocs.net/blog/@wishlee24/194/</link><description>
&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang="ko"&gt;
